### Test Refresh Token Endpoint
### First, login to get tokens
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "fbn7ym@tr.pte.hu",
  "password": "fbn7ym"
}

###
### Use the refreshToken from the login response to get new tokens
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJmYjczN2YzYi05NTk1LTQ1ZWYtOTU5Ni03MGRiNmYxNzBlYTMiLCJyb2xlIjoiU1RVREVOVCIsInRva2VuVHlwZSI6InJlZnJlc2giLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMzOTE1NjksImV4cCI6MTc3MzQ3Nzk2OX0.qYQKKEiayGOw4yM6pHoTnlVWWZTp67jl72ZiP79dQ-g"
}

###
### Logout – revokes the refresh token so it can never be used again.
### Body: same { "refreshToken": "..." } shape as /auth/refresh.
### Response: 204 No Content on success.
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJmYjczN2YzYi05NTk1LTQ1ZWYtOTU5Ni03MGRiNmYxNzBlYTMiLCJyb2xlIjoiU1RVREVOVCIsInRva2VuVHlwZSI6InJlZnJlc2giLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMzOTE1OTYsImV4cCI6MTc3MzQ3Nzk5Nn0.4sExc1MBhlEb406O-b1vEKke58XaggUUFl6X28KU-UU"
}

###
### Confirm the revoked token is rejected (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJmYjczN2YzYi05NTk1LTQ1ZWYtOTU5Ni03MGRiNmYxNzBlYTMiLCJyb2xlIjoiU1RVREVOVCIsInRva2VuVHlwZSI6InJlZnJlc2giLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMzOTE1OTYsImV4cCI6MTc3MzQ3Nzk5Nn0.4sExc1MBhlEb406O-b1vEKke58XaggUUFl6X28KU-UU"
}
